  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The formation of a rear dormer window and the installation of x3 rooflights to the front roofslope would be damaging to the roof form and architectural style of the main building.  These alterations proposed at roof level would be further damaging to the roofline of the short terrace which has a front and rear roofline highly visible from the street to the detriment of the character and appearance of the surrounding conservation area.  The proposal would conflict with policy 9 of the Draft Core Strategy, policies D1 (Overall Design), D4 (Designing in Context), D11 (Alterations & Extensions) and D25 (Roof Extensions) of the Unitary Development Plan (2002) and the guidance contained within the Islington Urban Design Guide (2006)."
